1
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:09,390
Hi, Michael. Hi, Danny.
你好,Michael.你好,Danny.

2
00:00:09,400 --> 00:00:10,000
Hi, Nancy.
你好,Nancy.

3
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:11,900
Yvonne, have you met our new tenants?
Yvonne,见过我们的新房客了吗?

4
00:00:11,950 --> 00:00:12,700
Not yet.
还没有.

5
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:15,200
Yvonne Washington, Michael Chung and Danny DeMarco. 
Yvonne Washington, Michael Chung和Danny DeMarco. 

6
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:16,500
They moved in last weekend. 
他们是上周末搬进来的.

7
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:19,300
It was last weekend, right?
是上周末,对吗?

8
00:00:19,460 --> 00:00:20,900
Just last Saturday.
就在上周六.

9
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:24,250
Of course. How could I forget that sofa?
当然.我怎么可能忘记那张沙发呢?

10
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:26,500
How did you finally get it into the apartment?
最后你们是怎么把它弄进房间的?

11
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:29,000
Very slowly and very carefully.
慢慢地,非常小心地搬进去的.

12
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:30,700
Yvonne, do you live here, too?
Yvonne,你也住这儿吗?

13
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:33,100
No, no. Nancy and I are business partners, 
不,不.Nancy和我是生意伙伴,

14
00:00:33,150 --> 00:00:34,507
so I'm here quite a bit.
所以我经常来这.

15
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:35,900
Oh. What kind of business?
Oh. 你们做哪一行?

16
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,500
Interior design. 
室内装潢设计.

17
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:39,400
Do you need help with your new place?
你们的新地方需要装修吗?

18
00:00:39,600 --> 00:00:42,500
With our furniture? Impossible!
就我们这些家具?不可能!

19
00:00:42,700 --> 00:00:44,900
Oh, I hardly think so.
Oh,我不这么认为.

20
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,400
You haven't seen the sofa.
你没见过我们的沙发.

21
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:50,900
Besides, I'm sure Lisa will help us redecorate.
而且,我相信Lisa会帮我们重新装饰的.

22
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:53,100
-Lisa?   -Lisa's my girlfriend.
-Lisa?   -Lisa是我的女朋友. 

23
00:00:53,300 --> 00:00:55,400
Just getting home from work, Danny?
刚下班回家吗,Danny?

24
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:57,250
Yeah. I'm beat.
是的.我累死了.

25
00:00:57,300 --> 00:00:58,586
Where do you work?
你在哪里工作?

26
00:00:58,600 --> 00:01:00,600
Kinko's. The night shift.
在Kinko复印社.夜班.

27
00:01:00,700 --> 00:01:02,100
You too, Michael?
你也是吗,Michael?

28
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:05,300
Oh no. Michael is a serious film maker.
Oh不是.Michael可是位严肃的电影制片人.

29
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:07,500
-Danny...   -Really?
-Danny...   -真的吗?

30
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:09,600
I'm a graduate student in Film Studies.
我是研究生,电影研究专业.

31
00:01:09,650 --> 00:01:11,200
And I do work at night, occasionally.
有时晚上我也打些工.

32
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:13,700
Actually, Yvonne, we've got to run. 
真的,Yvonne,我们得走了.

33
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:15,766
Everything OK in the apartment?
公寓的情况都好吗?

34
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:16,600
So far, so good.
到目前为止还行.

35
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,200
Good. We'll see you later.
好.那再见了.

36
00:01:18,250 --> 00:01:19,200
-Nice to meet you.  -Bye.
-很高兴认识你们.    -再见.

37
00:01:20,300 --> 00:01:22,100
It must be hard to work all night.
整夜工作一定很累.

38
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:24,200
Unless you sleep all day.
除非你白天睡一整天.

